### 1. Complete Josh Comeau Custom CSS Reset (Copy-Paste Ready)

```css
/*
  Josh's Custom CSS Reset
  https://www.joshwcomeau.com/css/custom-css-reset/
*/

*, *::before, *::after {
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

*:not(dialog) {
  margin: 0;
}

@media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
  html {
    interpolate-size: allow-keywords;
  }
}

body {
  line-height: 1.5;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
}

img, picture, video, canvas, svg {
  display: block;
  max-width: 100%;
}

input, button, textarea, select {
  font: inherit;
}

p, h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
  overflow-wrap: break-word;
}

p {
  text-wrap: pretty;
}
h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
  text-wrap: balance;
}

#root, #__next {   /* Apne project ke root element ke hisaab se change karo */
  isolation: isolate;
}
```

### 2. Har Rule Ka Simple Explanation

| Rule / Group                          | Kya Karta Hai?                                                                 | Kyun Zaroori Hai? |
|---------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------|-------------------|
| `*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }` | Width/height mein padding + border include karta hai                          | No unexpected overflow, predictable layout |
| `*:not(dialog) { margin: 0; }`        | Default margins hata deta hai (except dialog)                                  | Aap khud spacing control kar sako |
| `interpolate-size: allow-keywords` (with media query) | `height: 0` se `height: auto` smooth animate karne deta hai                   | Accordion, dropdowns etc. ke liye modern animation |
| `body { line-height: 1.5; }`          | Text lines ke beech better spacing                                             | Readability badhti hai (dyslexia friendly) |
| `-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased` | macOS par text ko sharp aur clean banata hai                                   | Better text rendering on Apple devices |
| `img, picture, video, canvas, svg { display: block; max-width: 100%; }` | Media elements ko block banao + container se bahar na jaye                   | No unwanted gaps, responsive by default |
| `input, button, textarea, select { font: inherit; }` | Form controls parent ka font use karein                                        | Consistent typography, no mobile zoom |
| `overflow-wrap: break-word`           | Lamba text (URLs, codes) container se bahar na jaye                            | Prevents horizontal scroll |
| `text-wrap: pretty` (on p)            | Paragraphs ka last line better balance karta hai                               | Clean aur professional look |
| `text-wrap: balance` (on headings)    | Headings ke lines equal length mein wrap karein                                | Headings visually balanced lagte hain |
| `isolation: isolate` (on #root)       | Root element par naya stacking context banata hai                              | Modals, tooltips, popovers ka z-index easy ho jata hai |

### 3. Quick Tips from Josh

- Yeh reset **unopinionated** hai — design ke baare mein kuch nahi kehta, sirf baseline fix karta hai.
- Apne framework ke hisaab se root selector change karo (`#root`, `#__next`, `.app` etc.).
- Treat this as **starting point** — apne project ke hisaab se modify kar sakte ho.
- `prefers-reduced-motion` respect karta hai accessibility ke liye.
- New CSS features (`text-wrap`, `interpolate-size`) progressive enhancement hain.

### 4. Comparison with Previous Resets (Aapke Series ke Hisaab Se)

- **Eric Meyer Reset** → Bahut aggressive (sab zero).
- **Normalize.css** → Gentle, defaults preserve karta hai.
- **Matt Brictson Hybrid** → Similar direction.
- **Josh Comeau** → Sabse modern + thoughtful (2026 tak updated) — readability + new CSS properties focus.
